cu.explanation_en: Changed MNC from 1 to 0, which is out of range for valid MNC values (typically 01-99 for 2-digit, 001-999 for 3-digit), causing PLMN configuration errors.

du.explanation_en: Changed MNC from 1 to 0, which is out of range for valid MNC values (typically 01-99 for 2-digit, 001-999 for 3-digit), causing PLMN configuration errors.
du.explanation_zh: 将MNC从1更改为0，这超出了有效MNC值的范围（通常为2位数的01-99，3位数的001-999），导致PLMN配置错误。
